graph.name: 109_nist_synthetic_polymer_maldi_recipes_database_tree
graph.pubchem_source_name: NIST Synthetic Polymer MALDI Recipes Database
pubchem_description: NIST Synthetic Polymer MALDI Recipes Database consists of methods for matrix-assisted laser desorption ionization (MALDI) mass spectrometry on a wide variety of synthetic polymers. The classification is based on polymer group, IUPAC classes, and individual polymers, and matrix compounds used for MALDI.
